{"tid":1199293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆料網媒: 香港人若與全球華人合作「反送中」, 可把習近平送終","createTime":"2019-06-10T12:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T13:22:33.000Z","uid":134071,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e47fe2b065f6f3fee10ab23a3fa4265b686f6c","tid":1199293,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:36:26.000Z","msg":"網絡媒體「海風快報」在月前曾爆料揭中國5年改建300座監獄,&nbsp; 質疑是要轉移在囚維吾爾人.<br />\n<br />\n(而且「海風快報」經常支持Trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/5xyxh/status/1137508932933554176\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F5xyxh%2Fstatus%2F1137508932933554176&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=0ef489cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F5xyxh%2Fstatus%2F1137508932933554176&h=ca92fc6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/5xyxh/status/1137508932933554176</a><br />\n<br />\n海風快報<br />\n&rlm;<br />\n海風：不要小看6.9港人反送中抗議事件，這很有可能演變成一場給習近平的送終事件。究竟是&ldquo;送中&rdquo;還是&ldquo;送終&rdquo;，這不僅要靠港人的努力，還要有全體華人的積極參與。<strong>只要全球華人形成共識，再加上國際社會的助力，最終就會成為一場給習近平給中共偽政權的送終事件。</strong>"},{"pid":"bd90688b5903e8f0cf49a8e50c26cb0d4cb632f2","tid":1199293,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627aa9da5b243ed5dc4bc0881ae1df45551d1fd7","tid":1199293,"uid":67043,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:46:54.000Z","msg":"要演變成反共，反極權運動"},{"pid":"b615c19e57b4321662e60b5da4f2a4bcce3bb286","tid":1199293,"uid":213877,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:59:02.000Z","msg":"咁睇得起香港人"},{"pid":"94902fb1ca811b246290bb9effbea3c5790bc483","tid":1199293,"uid":84633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:00:49.000Z","msg":"一盤很大的棋"},{"pid":"0151c5e54bcf2fc8c7b5738920e399551276e3b7